<DATELINE>SANTA ANA, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A former state Highway Patrol officer
was sentenced to eight years in prison for running a brothel near
the popular Huntington Beach Pier.
   William Scott Taylor pleaded guilty last month to 29 sex-related
carges, including pimping, pandering and engaging in lewd and
